snippet.title: Chicken Fight - Gameplay Reveal Trailer (Wishlist Now)
snippet.description:
Join the Discord for news and early access: https://discord.gg/xgDZKesnJC
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2159470/Chicken_Fight/

Thank you to "Kazoozi" for the music, his twitch linked here: https://www.twitch.tv/kazoozi

Chicken Fight is a platformer beat 'em up where you utilize your environment to defeat your enemies who consist of mutant frogs, werewolves, and even other chickens. There is a variety of modes, maps and gamemodes to play for everyone to enjoy.

This trailer is made up of clips of earlier builds of the game, what is shown may not be final.





multipalyer
